Let me help
1- Juanito Laguna flies a newspaper kite
2- spiced rhum drink
3- Earthen urn
4- Sicuriadas (sicuri is a type of pan pipe. a "sicuriada" is a musical form)
6- Cueca (chilean dance) Let go my sleeve/wandering musician
12- a Letter to El Che
13- a tear
14 Cueca of the CUT (Central Unica de trabajadores: Workers unitary Union)

Cheers.
